Question: Do you think the Federal Government should provide free healthcare?
Answer:
from my standpoint of view, i would vote for the free healthcare for everyone. the reasons are as below. firstly, healthcare is a very complicated issue now for it refers to many factors which requires a lot of money and people to carry the plans out. why do not use the money to be a part of the free healthcare. secondly, if the government could provide free healthcare and apply higher tax for high income populations, there will be a guarantee for everyone to see doctors without concerns.